      "content": "Hey, I'm studying for my con law exam and honestly getting super confused. When looking at the recent Supreme Court rulings on the 2nd amendment, do you think they are actually following the Founders' original intent, or is this just a case of judicial overreach/activism? Like, is there a real legal basis for it or is it just politics?",
