      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, really? I thought the whole point of the \"originalist\" argument was that the Court *is* sticking to the original meaning to avoid activism. If you're saying the current rulings are activism, aren't you saying that the originalist interpretation of the 2nd Amendment is actually just a modern political tool rather than a legitimate legal theory?",
